# 🔍 RAKSHA AI — WhatsApp Chat Scanner Feature

**Module Codename: KAVACH-WA (WhatsApp Guard)**
Integrate real WhatsApp chat scanning into the RAKSHA AI platform. Users connect their WhatsApp by scanning a QR code (powered by `whatsapp-web.js`), the backend reads their chats, and Groq-powered AI analyses every conversation for scams, fraud, phishing, threats, and suspicious patterns — flagging dangerous messages in a beautiful dashboard.

